球磨川有11处河岸被淹没，1处[[决堤|决堤]]<ref name=kyodonews2>{{Cite web|url=https://english.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/1b3d8f7c26a5-flooded-southwestern-japan-gets-more-rain-as-rescue-efforts-continue.html|title=Southwestern Japan hit by more heavy rain as death toll rises to 49|website=Kyodo News+|date=2020-07-06|accessdate=2020-07-08|archive-date=2020-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200707133610/https://english.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/1b3d8f7c26a5-flooded-southwestern-japan-gets-more-rain-as-rescue-efforts-continue.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。救援直升机在球磨村救助被冲散的居民<ref name="ABCAU" />。[[蘆北町|蘆北町]]有八处民宅被冲破<ref name="BBCJuly4" />。[[津奈木町|津奈木町]]有2到3人从[[泥石流|泥石流]]中被救出，但无生命迹象<ref name=ABCAU/>。[[九州电力|九州电力]]表示，熊本县和鹿儿岛县有约8000户停电<ref name="ABCAU" />。另有6100座房屋被淹，11座桥梁被毁<ref>{{Cite web|title= Southwestern Japan hit by more heavy rain as death toll rises to 49|url= https://english.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/1b3d8f7c26a5-flooded-southwestern-japan-gets-more-rain-as-rescue-efforts-continue.html|dead-url= no|accessdate= 2020-07-07|work= Kyodo News|archive-date= 2020-07-07|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200707133610/https://english.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/1b3d8f7c26a5-flooded-southwestern-japan-gets-more-rain-as-rescue-efforts-continue.html}}</ref>，4700座建筑遭损毁或冲破<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2020-07-08|title=Torrential rain lashes Japan, 870,000 urged to evacuate|url=https://english.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/eca5f4a2c615-torrential-rain-lashes-central-japan-warning-issued-in-gifu-nagano.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709014949/https://english.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/eca5f4a2c615-torrential-rain-lashes-central-japan-warning-issued-in-gifu-nagano.html|archive-date=2020-07-09|access-date=2020-07-09|website=Kyodo News+|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[人吉市|人吉市]]附近[[決堤|決堤]]。当地漂流协会的志愿者用筏子营救被洪水围困的当地民众。至少17名当地人遇难<ref>{{cite news |title= Japanese rafters paddle against the floods amid torrential Kyushu rains |url= https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asia/japan-rain-flood-kyushu-island-kuma-river-raft-rescue-12908644 |agency= AFP |publisher= Channel News Asia |date= 2020-07-07 |accessdate= 2020-07-10 |archive-date= 2020-07-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200708141709/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asia/japan-rain-flood-kyushu-island-kuma-river-raft-rescue-12908644 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name=kyodonews/><ref name= ABCAU/>。

