== 影响 ==
洪水中断了日本工业重镇九州地区的经济活动。[[丰田汽车|丰田汽车]]、[[佳能|佳能]]和[[松下电器|松下电器]]出于员工安全考虑，临时暂停生产<ref>{{Cite web|title=Deadly Japan floods halt factories across industrial base Kyushu|url=https://asia.nikkei.com/Economy/Natural-disasters/Deadly-Japan-floods-halt-factories-across-industrial-base-Kyushu|accessdate=2020-07-07|work=Nikkei Asian Review|archive-date=2020-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200707222736/https://asia.nikkei.com/Economy/Natural-disasters/Deadly-Japan-floods-halt-factories-across-industrial-base-Kyushu|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不过，[[內閣官房長官|內閣官房長官]][[菅义伟|菅义伟]]6日发表声明，表示不希望主要供应链中断<ref name="Reuters7" />。

鉴于当前的[[2019冠状病毒病日本疫情|COVID-19日本疫情]]，被撤离的民众和当地官员关心庇护中心的问题<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Local gov'ts fret over coronavirus spread at shelters after torrential rain|url=https://english.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/65bfb5d12e23-local-govts-fret-over-virus-spread-at-shelters-after-torrential-rain.html|dead-url=no|accessdate=2020-07-07|work=Kyodo News|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729175704/https://english.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/65bfb5d12e23-local-govts-fret-over-virus-spread-at-shelters-after-torrential-rain.html}}</ref>。民众前往中心庇护前需测量体温，或被要求前往其他中心，确保[[保持社交距离|保持社交距离]]。部分撤离民众选择在自己的车子中避难，或到朋友家暂避<ref name=":0" />。这些措施遵循了政府官员预测到洪水和疾病传播可能引发“双重灾难”所制定的建议<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite news|last=Reynolds|first=Isabel|date=2020-06-22|title=Japan Braces for Double Disaster of Covid Outbreaks at Flooding Shelters|publisher=Bloomberg|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-06-22/japan-braces-for-double-disaster-of-covid-at-flooding-shelters|accessdate=2020-07-07|archive-date=2020-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709213423/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-06-22/japan-braces-for-double-disaster-of-covid-at-flooding-shelters|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

